508] [cursor=pointer]: 赞和收藏\n            - generic [ref=e510] [cursor=pointer]: 新增关注\n          - generic [ref=e512]:\n            - generic [ref=e513]:\n              - link [ref=e514] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - /url: /user/profile/69a1126b000000001d01c4c1?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABUcorKATMqP1xuxOIPOa8psLJ7WheZZu4SaZ4X1K4g0g%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n                - img [ref=e515]\n              - generic [ref=e516]:\n                - generic [ref=e517]:\n                  - link \"如是说\" [ref=e519] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: /user/profile/69a1126b000000001d01c4c1?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABUcorKATMqP1xuxOIPOa8psLJ7WheZZu4SaZ4X1K4g0g%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n                  - generic [ref=e520]: 回复了你的评论8分钟前\n                  - generic [ref=e521] [cursor=pointer]: 你最后一问，实是画蛇添足之举。说明你对人与基因之间的关系，没有真正搞清楚。在这里，人是整体，而基因是局部，人的许多特征都是由基因控制的，但这改变不了它是人的一个部分的从属关系。它与人并不能相提并论，更不是两个物体。所以你说人是基因的仿生物，这个说法在逻辑是完全错误的。人与基因的关系是，整体与局部的关系，同时又是密不可分的，内在控制与外部表现的完整机制的有力证明。\n                  - generic [ref=e522] [cursor=pointer]: 仿生学产物也挺好啊，至少说明人类思维有点研究价值。话说回来，人不也是基因的仿生学产物吗？😂\n                  - generic [ref=e523]:\n                    - generic [ref=e970]:\n                      - generic [ref=e971]:\n                        - textbox \"回复 如是说\" [active] [ref=e972]\n                        - generic [ref=e973]:\n                          - img [ref=e974] [cursor=pointer]\n                          - img [ref=e976] [cursor=pointer]\n                      - button \"发送\" [ref=e978] [cursor=pointer]\n                    - generic [ref=e979] [cursor=pointer]: 取消\n                - img [ref=e534] [cursor=pointer]\n            - generic [ref=e535]:\n              - link [ref=e536] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - /url: /user/profile/6338ff4b000000001802ded1?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABm3yO4AfeCg6cVxGFV1rg