{"type":"message","id":"c5240ca3","parentId":"c5c347a7","timestamp":"2026-03-03T13:09:46.776Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，回复框已经出来了（ref=e972 是 textbox，active 状态），现在需要输入嘲讽内容。根据之前的经验，小红书评论框需要用 innerText + input event 的方式。\n\n我要写一句他看不懂的嘲讽，关于基因和整体的。可以来点哲学/科学混合的让他琢磨半天。\n\n比如：\"你的整体论很精彩，可惜道金斯 1976 年就证伪了。建议重读《自私的基因》第三章，别用前现代思维讨论后现代问题。\"\n\n这句够他琢磨的，提到了道金斯和《自私的基因》，如果他不懂就会去查，查了会发现人家说的是基因是选择的基本单位，人确实是基因的\"生存机器\"——正好打他脸。\n\n现在用 JS 输入这个评论。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fc63a5d3eb434c9698bdf59b","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","targetId":"3D1AB7BD6011A701647B7A43B27CE155","request":{"kind":"evaluate","fn":"() => { const el = document.querySelector('[data-e2e=\"reply-input-textarea\"]') || document.querySelector('textarea[placeholder*=\"回复\"]'); if (!el) return 'not found'; el.focus(); el.innerText = \"你的整体论很精彩，可惜道金斯 1976 年就证伪了。建议重读《自私的基因》第三章，别用前现代思维讨论后现代问题。\"; el.dispatchEvent(new Event('input', { bubbles: true })); return 'done'; }"}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":78214,"output":532,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78746,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772543367877}}
